By: Iso-no-Kami-no Yakatsugu
---
The esoteric teachings of Buddhism and the tenets of the outsiders are after
all one and the same in essence. At a cursory glance the latter may seem
strange and incompatible with the former; yet, tactfully utilized, there is no
conflicting difference at all between them.
